<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EcoMind</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8a2be2, #ff69b4, #1e90ff);
        margin: 0;
        overflow: hidden;
        height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
      }
      .container {
        background-color: white;
        display: flex;
        border-radius: 20px;
      }
      .image-container {
        background: url("https://img.freepik.com/free-vector/liquid-style-background_23-2148476933.jpg")
          no-repeat;
        background-size: auto 100%;
        background-position: center;
        background-repeat: no-repeat;
        height: 600px;
        width: 600px;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
      }
      .image-contents {
        text-align: center;
        color: white;
        position: relative;
        left: -100%; /* Start off-screen to the left */
        opacity: 0; /* Initially invisible */
        animation: slideInFromLeft 0.5s forwards, fadeIn 1s forwards; /* Combine slide and fade animations */
      }

      @keyframes slideInFromLeft {
        0% {
          left: -100%; /* Start off-screen to the left */
        }
        100% {
          left: 0; /* Slide in to the left */
        }
      }

      @keyframes fadeIn {
        0% {
          opacity: 0; /* Start invisible */
        }
        100% {
          opacity: 1; /* Fade in to visible */
        }
      }
      .image-container > .image-contents > h3 {
        font-size: 20px;
        margin: 10;
      }
      .image-container > .image-contents > h1 {
        margin: 10;
        margin-top: 0;
        font-size: 35px;
      }
      .image-container > .image-contents > h1 > span {
        color: #007fc4;
      }
      .image-container > .image-contents > p {
        margin: 0px 50px;
        text-align: justify;
        line-height: 1.5;
      }
      .login-container {
        width: 25vw;
        padding: 50px;
        background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        position: relative;
        right: -100%;
        opacity: 0;
        animation: slideInFromRight 0.5s forwards, fadeIn 1s forwards;
      }

      @keyframes slideInFromRight {
        0% {
          right: -100%;
        }
        100% {
          right: 0;
        }
      }

      @keyframes fadeIn {
        0% {
          opacity: 0;
        }
        100% {
          opacity: 1;
        }
      }
      .login-container > h2 {
        font-size: 45px;
        color: #007fc4;
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 50px;
      }
      .login-container > h3 {
        color: rgb(88, 86, 86);
        font-size: 18px;
        margin: 20px;
        margin-left: 0;
      }
      input {
        width: 100%;
        padding: 10px;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
        border: 1px solid #ddd;
        border-radius: 5px;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }
      button {
        width: 100%;
        padding: 10px;
        background-color: #667eea;
        color: white;
        border: none;
        border-radius: 5px;
        cursor: pointer;
        transition: background-color 0.3s;
      }
      button:hover {
        background-color: #764ba2;
      }
      h5 {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: end;
      }
      h5 > a {
        text-decoration: none;
        color: #667eea;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-size: 15px;
      }
      .login-link {
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 20px;
      }
      .login-link > a {
        text-decoration: none;
        color: #667eea;
        font-size: 20px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="image-container">
        <div class="image-contents">
          <h3>Nice to meet you</h3>
          <h1>Welcome to Eco<span>Mind</span></h1>
          <p>
            Discover EcoMind, where your voice finds its community. Whether
            you're here to explore, inspire, or connect with kindred spirits,
            this platform is your canvas for expression. Share your stories,
            ideas, and reflections in a space crafted for genuine interaction
            and meaningful exchanges. Let your thoughts shape narratives, ignite
            conversations, and cultivate empathy. Embark on a journey of
            exploration, where each perspective enriches our collective tapestry
            of ideas. Embrace the impact of sharing, because here, every voice
            makes a difference.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="login-container">
        <h2>Register Here!</h2>
        <h3>Enter your Details:-</h3>

        <form method="post" action="/register/post">
          <input type="text" placeholder="Full Name" name="username" required />
          <input type="email" placeholder="Email" name="email" required />
          <input
            type="password"
            placeholder="Password"
            name="password"
            required
          />
          <button type="submit">Register</button>
        </form>
        <div class="login-link">
          <a href="/login">Already have an account? Login</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
